description:
A modern outdoor classic, the plushy softness of a Synchilla fleece is a welcome layer of warmth on a cool morning or at a shady campsite. It has Patagonia's signature Snap-T styling: chest pocket with a snapped nylon flap and a stand-up collar to top the 4-snap placket. Contrast spandex binding at sleeve openings and hem helps hold in warmth.Double-faced polyester fleece is soft, warm and lightweight.Stand-up collar guards against gusts of wind.Nylon placket has four snaps for versatile venting.Chest pocket with nylon flap and snap closure.Spandex trim on hem and cuffs helps keep out the cold.Sewn-in name tag has multiple spaces to accommodate hand-me-downs.

